pagerduty

This Module automatise the deployment of pd-nag-connector available at
https://github.com/jeffwalter/pd-nag-connector
And is a fork of https://github.com/KrisBuytaert/puppet-pagerduty-icinga

It is possible to configure the class with the following parameter:

class { 'pagerduty':
  servicekey                   => 'pagerduty API key',
  service_notification_period  => '24x7',
  host_notification_period     => '24x7',
  service_notification_options => 'w,u,c,r,f',
  host_notification_options    => 'd,u,r,f',
  monitoring_cfg_path          => '/path',
  monitoring_user              => 'icinga_user',
  monitoring_group             => 'icinga_group',
  command_file                 => '/path/command_file',
  status_file                  => '/path/status_file',
  manage_packages              => 'yes',
  use_proxy                    => 'no',
  proxy_proto                  => 'https',
  proxy                        => 'https://yourproxy:port',
}

